{"title":"春开酒坛（外一首）","authors":["林染"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":7,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春开酒坛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"·林染·"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新房在梧桐树下盖起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门楣上的红联"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜盈盈地说着话“春开酒坛”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是第一次，我家终于有屋瓦了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响晴的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姥姥例外地手搭凉篷，看天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祈雨的手，雨偏偏作对"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨只喜欢漏雨的茅屋顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今天，直到黄昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点滴也没有落下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫桑椹白桑椹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九九雨燕来雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕的后面桑椹来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村童们像黑夜的麻雀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没头没脑地碰着树枝飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿歌在树上熟透了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫桑椹白桑椹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗颗清亮的铃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桑树是颤颤悠悠的马儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打马过童年，涉春荒，走水灾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满身的小铃铛一路响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫桑椹白桑椹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨点一样，把鸟雀们的嘴巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打进深深的农历里"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}